      <article id="summary">
        <h4 class="section-heading">Summary</h4>
        <div class="summary">
          <p><em>The Grand Budapest Hotel</em>&nbsp;recounts the adventures of Gustave H,&nbsp;a legendary concierge at a famous European hotel between the wars,&nbsp;and Zero Moustafa, the lobby boy who becomes his most trusted friend.</p>

<p>The story involves the theft and recovery of a priceless Renaissance painting&nbsp;and the battle for an enormous family fortune -- all against the back-drop of&nbsp;a suddenly and dramatically changing Continent.</p>
        </div>
        <h5 class="summary-toggle"><a href="javascript:void(0)">Show Full Summary</a></h5>
