              <h5>"The Grand Budapest Hotel": Review</h5>
              <p>As much as "The Grand Budapest Hotel" takes on the aspect of a cinematic confection, it does so to grapple with the very raw and real stuff of humanity from an unusual but highly illuminating angle.</p>
